entries.femaleVariant: C'mon, what's the matter? What's goin' on?
OK, 'cept, nothin' I can do if you don't tell me.
Oh, man, you're screwin' with my head!
There's that tone! Yelling comes easy! Takin' me out somewhere – that fucking borders on the impossible!
I'm not yelling! Said yourself we got everything here – chooms, stores, eateries!
And that's all you've ever dreamed of? OK. Good to know.
